item.title: All their work is done dilligently!
item.description: I’ve hired Sal’s Services on multiple occasions for everything from yard work and housekeeping tasks, to baked goods, and art. All work is done diligently and completely, exceeds expectations for quality, and their employees are professional and pleasant!
